Subject: Hyperbolic Corridor Navigator

Description: Contract for moving attention through a higher-dimensional hyperbolic field by selecting peripheral frames, extending local awareness, and treating curving association as correlation until identity resolves.

@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\source_documents\2026-06-24_hyperbolic_corridor_navigator\Dictated_Hyperbolic_Corridor_Navigator_Source.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\SevenFoldPantsCorrelationFrame.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\HyperbolicPantsAttentionMap.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\AttentionTraversalPolicy.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\FocusZoom.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\ApertureReentryCycle.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\PeripheryDimensionalProbe.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\AttentionBalanceCenter.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\SecurityHonestyGovernance.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\Wisdom.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\Caution.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\source_documents\2026-06-24_corridor_navigator_runtime\Derived_Corridor_Navigator_Runtime_Source.sop
